external_knowledge:
; Home team win is denoted by 'H' in the full_time_result column; 
; Away team win is denoted by 'A' in the full_time_result column; 
; Draw is denoted by 'D' in the full_time_result column; 
; Yellow cards and red cards are types of penalties given to players in a football match; 
; Betting odds represent the likelihood of a particular outcome in a match.

sql:
SELECT match_id
FROM betting_summary
WHERE total_bets = (SELECT MAX(total_bets) FROM betting_summary);

external_knowledge:
A team 'winning at home' means that the full-time result is 'H' (Home Win); 
A 'top team' refers to a team with a higher rank, i.e., a lower rank number; 
The ranking is based on average shots on target;
The average shots on target is the total shots on target divided by the total number of matches.

sql:
SELECT match_id
FROM matches
ORDER BY match_date DESC;
